Author: Karim Ardalan
Summary: Manage your case studies and success stories using the Case Studies web app. Upload a photo, add a PDF and more.

Author: Karim Ardalan
Summary: This is the most popular web app we’ve ever created. We use it on almost every website. It allows you to easily display a list of photos on the home page and slide from one to the next.

Summary: With the Job Postings web app you can easily publish job openings on your website and even allow visitors to apply and submit their resume.

Summary: Add a dynamic list of Press Releases to your website. You can even attach a PDF copy of each press release.

Author: Karim Ardalan
Summary: Proximity search is a great feature of Business Catalyst. You can use this web app to display a list of closest locations. We’ve used this for Store Locators, Office Locations, Distributor Search and more.

Item Description: The Team Web App allows you to have a database of staff available on your website. You can add a photo, bio and even social media links for each person. The staff members can even be classified into Management, Personnel, etc.

Summary: A useful web app for almost any website. You can store a list of testimonials and then rotate them throughout your website.
